U.K. Advises Nationals Against Travel to Bahrain on Unrest

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-03-15T22:56:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-15/u-k-advises-nationals-against-travel-to-bahrain-on-unrest.html
The U.K. is advising British
nationals against traveling to Bahrain and for those in the
country to leave “as soon as it is safe to do so,” as a result
of unrest in the country and the declared state of emergency.
The Foreign and Commonwealth Office made a statement on its
 website  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 